{% extends "emails/template_transactional.twig" %}
{% block body %}
    <p>Hi there {{ registration.first_name }}!</p>

    <p>Thank you for registering as a mentor for CodeDay. This email confirms that we're planning to see you on
       {{ registration.event.starts_at|date('F j, Y') }}.</p>

    <p>Unless you've already committed to a specific time, you're welcome to arrive any time between 2pm and midnight
       on Saturday, {{ registration.event.starts_at|date('F j') }}. You're welcome to stay as long as you want, but
       please plan to stay at least 2 hours. Help is particularly appreciated in the evenings.</p>

    <p>You will receive a reminder email with address and contact information closer to the event.
       <a href="https://codeday.training.srnd.org/mentors.html" target="_blank">Whenever you have the chance, please
       read our mentor guide.</a></p>

    <p>We're looking forward to seeing you soon! Please reply to this email if you have any questions.</p>
{% endblock %}
